snippet.title: Fentanyl Addict interview -Amber
snippet.description:
Fentanyl Addict interview -Amber



( WATCH IN HD! 1080p )

For those viewers of this channel who have been asking for a way to help...
If you are interested in helping out, please feel free to send all donations to AML Films at:


AML Films
P.O. Box 39076
Philadelphia Pa 19136


Please do NOT send any sharps, money, checks, money orders, or any other monetary donations.


Thank You,    


We Out There




These adults come from different parts of the country and are struggling with addiction in Philadelphia. They agree to share their insights and experiences with drug addiction.
